{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/extras/Story_Icon.png?t=1737957420\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WISHLIST THE GAME TODAY!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this dystopian action-adventure, Benji Freese awakes to find himself imprisoned by a cunning, sadistic computer AI. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tortured and given no other options, he reluctantly accepts the computer's dangerous mission in hopes of regaining his precious freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/extras/Kickstarter_Titled_Capsule__resized_.png?t=1737957420\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of Benji as he travels to the most spine-chilling parts of the galaxy battling ruthless mercenaries, horrific undead creatures, and murderous cyborgs bent on stopping him in his path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/extras/Gameplay_Icon.png?t=1737957420\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Benji and the Crystal of Light </i>employs a system of <strong>movement-based combat </strong>inspired by legendary games like <strong><i>Doom</i></strong><i> </i>and <strong><i>Cuphead</i></strong>. But <strong>running and gunning</strong> isn't the only thing that is demanded of you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hack computers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Repair equipment </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in gripping <strong>dialogue menus</strong>\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And <strong>collect scrap metal</strong> to <strong>upgrade your arsenal</strong> and defend yourself in this sci-fi nightmare!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reclaim your freedom in the ultimate quest to find a mysterious artifact known as &quot;The Crystal of Light.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/extras/Music_Icon.png?t=1737957420\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The musical score to <i>Benji and the Crystal of Light</i> is an amalgamation of sounds from <strong>1980\u2019s</strong> <strong>science-fiction movies</strong> and <strong>ambient electronic music</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The electronic instruments and synthesizers harmonize to create a <strong>nostalgic, gloomy</strong> listening experience. Thus, the barrier between the player and Benji\u2019s lone-wolf journey is further dissolved.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">WISHLIST THE GAME TODAY!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737957420","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737957420","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737957420","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888240/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737957420","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"violence, blood, la